<div class="content means imeans" data-group="imeans" id="basicmean-wrapper">
    <h1><b class="title active" id="basicmean" data-group="imeans">基本释义</b><span class="seg"></span>
                <a href="javascript:watchit()" class="title disactive" data-for="detailmean">详细解释</a>
        <span class="seg"></span>
            </h1>
    <div class="tab-content">
    <p><strong>1. <a href="#dcrecucs">谷 [gǔ]</a></strong></p><dl><dt><a name="dcrecucs">谷 [gǔ]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>两山间的夹道或流水道，或指两山之间：山～。河～。</p></li><li><p>喻困境：进退维～（进退两难）。</p></li><li><p>庄稼和粮食的总称：五～。百～。</p></li><li><p>粟的别称，亦指稻的子实：～物。～米。稻～。</p></li><li><p>姓。</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
    </div>
    <div class="more-button">
